Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:01:59.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:07.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:09.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:22.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去蒼乃那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 傷口不會自己癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 夜禍的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會讓你來背我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:06.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭我背嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在想也許不會再有這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天這樣的天空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和依人相遇的那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是卷積雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是依人教我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,斷層雲 積雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,卷雲 層雲 積雲 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:37.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒能讓你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你已經讓我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看過的天空 你追逐的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,透過你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:03.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:09.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜禍的力量正在變弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 你留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我一個人不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再讓你看下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和蒼乃戰鬥時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還能相見的 一定還能相見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別說那種一眼就看穿的謊話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我也沒其它地方好去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我是必須要把性命獻給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為村子裡有惡靈作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你不可能做那樣的事 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這裡 總覺得明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會讓別人不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一個人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:00.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃的時候要笑出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起和你在一起時的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:38.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你教會了我什麼是心 人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以會痛苦 悲傷 難過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是總比不知道的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說漂亮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:48.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要把你變回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把必須接受依人死的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會如你所願的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就可以看到天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:46.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人 依人 依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 我不會再猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能把一切恢復原樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的生命給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:31.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:38.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:56.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我在最後許一次願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人一起看到的 那時的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,無法到達的 遙遠的約定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:10.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別問啦 別問啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來這裡躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:25.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來打算畫個天空的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點勉強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:36.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空 這就是… 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:38.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉總有一天會看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他自己偷看 又自己逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我一直想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你衣服的品味一年比一年差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋差點被扭下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:22.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 剛史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛史為什麼沒有逃走呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒理由逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 趁雨還沒停我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 剛史
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又是折紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是折不膩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 折紙其實很複雜的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把這裡折起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,折好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您親切的問候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名一直以來受你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是姊姊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依太可憐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 明明那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是一個粗野的姐姐啊 委屈你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:37.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都高二了 說過叫你也稍微學著沉著一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 為什麼我要被你們訓話啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請問要點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:55.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天推薦的是章魚和羅勒做的義大利冷麵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不像是在推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,點了的話好像會吃壞肚子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你也該打起精神來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事情都過了一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:17.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我覺得絕對不會再有比鬍子紳士更好的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,玩弄了我純潔的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,連招呼都不打一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就消失得無影無蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經聽膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,話說真名怎麼不回來打工呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她一個人是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:40.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想改變一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:47.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,改變什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:49.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比起錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想再長高點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,折好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 可不可以拿著這艘船的另一頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:48.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 請睜開眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓真名看的時候明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再多教我一點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:14.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是非常感謝你 能夠陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告訴我你的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃… 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,數學作業已經交了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,涼颼颼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是轉學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在看天空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡看到的天空很漂亮對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是晚霞很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天放學後都會到這裡來看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:46.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢 大概在以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我自己也不清楚 可就是覺得喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜歡天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這寬廣的天空把一切都連接起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把人 海 城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:22.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的另一面就是夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一個同樣連接在一起的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:36.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我會走在天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,走在那兩個人送給我的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 天空 喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:55.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:05.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊再不起來 太陽就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 快點起來 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:35.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像小依非常喜歡蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:43.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:58.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:00.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:10.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 明明把錢投進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:11.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:19.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:43.04,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(500,500)}sola
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何気ない言葉さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刻まれた胸が熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:30.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当たり前のように　過ごした日々が遠いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:35.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}かけがえのない人が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:40.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せに照らされて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:48.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しみさえ霞んでく幻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:54.02,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}やがて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Remember on my mind, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:05.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流れるあの雲に　心重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:13.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今を青く漂えば　愛しい君へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:20.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いだけが Ah... 伝わればいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:29.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も知らない未来　いつか会いたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:39.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その時を待ってる　見上げるあの空で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:56.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いだけが Ah... 伝わればいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:04.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何もいらない　ただねひとつの夢をね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:15.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感じてたと思うよ　見上げるあの空で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不經意的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在我心中蕩漾不已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:30.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}過去的日子　也理所當然地遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:35.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那無可取代的人兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:40.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正沐浴在幸福的陽光下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:48.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就連悲傷　和那朦朧的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:54.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也終於消逝在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:05.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們心心相映　在那流動的雲彩裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:13.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}倘若身駕祥雲　一定要去往心愛的你那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:20.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕只是一份心意　啊…　真想傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:29.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我們相遇　在那未知的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:39.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我等待在　這蒼穹之下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:56.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕只是一份心意　啊…　真想傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:04.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什麼都不需要了　這不過是一場夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:15.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我已經體味過了　在這蒼穹之下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:22.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽根が白く光り 眩しく飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:28.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心だけ乗せて欲しいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:36.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい手を伸ばす 届かない…知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:44.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどいま触れたい君に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:50.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}懐かしい風には あの頃の舟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:59.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幻が思い出を見せた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:08.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れない」誰かの声が切なく響く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:14.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}始まる予感にふるえて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:22.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れたい」願う自分がわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:33.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}待っている 揺られながら夢ひとつを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:22.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雪白閃亮的羽毛飛向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:28.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它要是能帶上我的心意該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:36.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出冰冷的雙手 明明知道觸摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:44.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可是現在還是想觸碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:50.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人懷念的微風像那時候的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:59.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}呈現出夢幻的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:08.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「無法忘懷」 某人悲傷的聲音迴響著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:14.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為即將開始的預感而顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:22.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「想要忘卻」 卻不明瞭如此祈願的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:33.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}帶著一個夢想和心中的動搖 等待你
